<div class="KonaBody"><p>Over 70 recipes to help you accomplish a wide variety of tasks in Linux quickly and efficiently.</p>
<p>Everything you need to know about Linux but were afraid to ask. This book will make you a master of the command line and teach you how to configure the network, write shell scripts, build a custom kernel, and much more.</p>
